    "improvements_made": "Added lookup tables for EMPLOYEE_STATUS and SALARY_GRADE to enforce enumeration consistency. Introduced EMPLOYEE_POSITION_HISTORY associative entity to capture temporal changes in position, department, and salary for audit and reporting. Retained EMPLOYEE.salary for cases where individual compensation deviates from the base salary, while keeping POSITION.base_salary for default values. Clarified one‑to‑one head_emp_id relationship and added created/updated timestamps. Removed the unnecessary REPORT entity, favoring views/stored procedures for reporting. All relationships were updated to reflect the new entities and to support hierarchy traversal, filtered queries, and salary calculations."
